{
  "version": 1,
  "principle": "sequenced_only",
  "notes": [
    "This file defines the preferred execution order for upcoming feature sprints/tracks in this repo.",
    "Items are intentionally sequenced (no parallel work) to minimize merge/conflict risk and schema churn.",
    "Each item should correspond to a triad-based feature directory under docs/project_management/next/<feature>/ with plan.md, tasks.json, session_log.md, specs, and kickoff prompts."
